    {
      "title": "Queue Depth",
      "description": "Number of click events waiting in the buffered channel.\n\nHealthy: fluctuates near 0, brief spikes during traffic bursts.\nUnhealthy: steadily climbing toward the buffer limit (10,000).\n\nIf it stays high, workers can't keep up. Solutions:\n- Increase WorkerCount\n- Increase BatchSize (fewer but larger DB writes)\n- Check DB write performance",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 27
      },
      "id": 9,
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
